#   Python3.11
#   Ubuntu 24.04 via WSL
#   OR
#   Ubuntu 22.04 via WSL
#   Vivado 2024.1 via WSL
#   NiFPGA Vivado 2021.1
#
# Usage:
#
# 1 - Install cboe_pitch
#   SETUPTOOLS_USE_DISTUTILS=stdlib python3 -m pip install -e .
#
# 2 - Install rest of Python dependencies
#   make install_deps
#
# 3 - Build
#   make simulate
#
